===Pokémon Sun and Pokémon Moon Special Demo Version===
{{main|Pokémon Sun and Pokémon Moon Special Demo Version}}
In the Special Demo, Professor Kukui takes the player, named [[Elio (game)|Sun]] to [[Ten Carat Hill]] to teach them all about Alola's [[island challenge|trials]]. He lends Sun a {{p|Pikachu}} to help perform in battle.
